is to keep bluffing,

77
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,200
disrupt their rhythm

78
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,240
and prevent them from going all-in.

79
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:28,600
When they think their chance has come,

80
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:31,060
we'll fold with a perfect hand and walk away.

81
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,080
I don't know

82
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,400
who my opponent is this time.

83
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,200
But I'm certain

84
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,040
she's not Ye Zhiqiu.

85
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,680
You came to me

86
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,840
because you know

87
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,600
