88
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:53,400
I can recognize them at a glance.

89
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,080
You

90
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,080
are just too clever.

91
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,360
So what's in it for me?

92
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,800
Are you going to rip me off?

93
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,400
You're so practical.

94
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,850
Whatever you think is right

95
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,960
