100
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,560
Right now,

101
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:28,040
I just want to live a simple life.

102
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,120
That's such a shame.

103
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:34,440
You chose to leave just when you should've blown up.

104
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,880
That takes real courage.

105
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,440
Actually,

106
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:41,440
I was hoping to get a job with you.

107
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,840
Since we're old classmates

108
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,720
and know each other well.

109
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,080
