110
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,400
After all, I've retired from the industry.

111
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,530
I don't have much say in these matters.

112
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:56,080
If I ever work on something again in the future,

113
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,540
I'll definitely call you.

114
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,680
Great.

115
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,240
