116
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:04,540
I hope this 'future' of yours isn't too far away.

117
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,210
Don't worry.

118
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:07,960
I'll be in touch.

119
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,920
Or I could contact you.

120
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,560
We know where to find each other now.

121
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,000
Alright.

122
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,010
I won't bother you then.

123
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,010
Goodbye.

124
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:23,920
Goodbye.

125
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,640
Xiangyang.

126
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,420
