129
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,000
Not at all.

130
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,300
Here to see Zhiqiu?

131
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,480
Yes.

132
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,720
I came to catch up with her.

133
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,640
