138
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,260
Xiangyang.

139
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,690
What are you doing here?

140
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,920
Since you're here,

141
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:09,000
I won't disturb your lovey-dovey time.

142
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,000
I'll be going now.

143
