You old classmates should get together more often.

144
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,480
That's fine.

145
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,640
We can also invite

146
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,640
Xie Yuxuan.

147
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,280
As for Leng Xiaoxiao,

148
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,440
forget it.

149
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,720
I'm leaving now.

150
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,160
Okay.

151
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:25,920
Call me.

152
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,610
You don't need to say anything.

153
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,480
I know.

154
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,360
Rachel Zhou left,

155
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,159
