156
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,320
Each one of them

157
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,240
has their own agenda.

158
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,140
Let's wait and see.

159
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,720
She definitely

160
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,080
wants something

161
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:53,300
