167
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,420
and wanted to become my agent.

168
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,240
But as a retired actor,

169
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,860
what do I need an agent for?

170
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,400
Haven't you

171
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:20,520
