190
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,280
Until you say yes.

191
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,600
Well done.

192
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:25,760
Keep him hanging.

193
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:28,490
