255
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,680
He even gave me some money for the funeral.

256
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:48,080
When Rachel died,

257
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:50,010
was Ye Zhiqiu there too?

258
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:52,520
She was completely shocked,

259
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:55,000
